snippet: Anna Fenninger overtook Lindsey Vonn in the super-G standings and closed in on Tina Maze atop the overall World Cup standings with a victory in Bulgaria.
abstract: Anna Fenninger of Austria wins super-G World Cup event at Bansko, Bulgaria, overtaking Lindsey Vonn in overall standings.
lead_paragraph: Anna Fenninger overtook Lindsey Vonn in the super-G standings and closed in on Tina Maze atop the overall World Cup standings with a victory in Bulgaria.

headline.main: Austrian Fenninger on the Rise in Standings
